---
title: "Petition for Orby to have character rights"
date: 2025-06-15
---
While I THE AUTHOR, do not think that Orby deserves or should have character rights, a growing number of people seem to disagree with that fact. To prevent further emails about the matter, here is a petition. If by some miracle of Kyuu above, it manages to reach 100 signatures, I will give Orby character rights.
https://www.change.org/p/grant-character-rights-to-orby
